🧱 🛑 STRICT ARCHITECTURE RULES (DO NOT BREAK THESE)
🔌 1. SOCKET RULES (REALTIME LAYER)

📁 src/socket/

✅ ALLOWED
emit events
listen events
socket connection
event constants
middleware (auth, retry)
❌ FORBIDDEN
React code (hooks, JSX)
game logic (cards, rules)
UI state
API calls (REST)
🧠 RULE

“Socket only moves data, never decides meaning.”

🎮 2. GAME ENGINE RULES

📁 src/game/

✅ ALLOWED
card logic
shuffle / deal / rules
animations
game state calculations
Phaser scenes / objects
❌ FORBIDDEN
socket.emit / socket.on
React state (use store instead)
API calls
UI components
🧠 RULE

“Game folder does NOT know network exists.”

🧠 3. STORE RULES (GLOBAL STATE)

📁 src/store/

✅ ALLOWED
player state
room state
game state
UI state (loading, modal, etc)
❌ FORBIDDEN
direct socket calls
DOM manipulation
game logic calculations
🧠 RULE

“Store only stores, it does NOT compute game logic.”

⚛️ 4. CONTEXT RULES (REACT BRIDGE ONLY)

📁 src/context/

✅ ALLOWED
SocketProvider
GameProvider
auth/session provider
❌ FORBIDDEN
business logic
game rules
socket event logic
🧠 RULE

“Context is plumbing, not logic.”

🌐 5. SERVICES RULES (API ONLY)

📁 src/services/

✅ ALLOWED
REST API calls
HTTP requests
backend communication (non-socket)
❌ FORBIDDEN
socket logic
game logic
UI state
🧠 RULE

“Services talk to backend, not to game.”

🧩 6. TYPES RULES (GLOBAL CONTRACTS)

📁 src/types/

✅ ALLOWED
Player type
Room type
GameState type
Socket event types
❌ FORBIDDEN
functions
constants
logic
🧠 RULE

“Types describe data only, nothing else.”

🧰 7. UTILS RULES

📁 src/utils/

✅ ALLOWED
pure helper functions
formatting
random generators
validation
❌ FORBIDDEN
socket usage
state usage
game rules (those belong in game/)
🧠 RULE

“Utils must be pure functions (no side effects).”

🎨 8. COMPONENT RULES

📁 src/components/

✅ ALLOWED
UI only
props-based logic
animations triggers (not logic)
❌ FORBIDDEN
socket logic
game rules
store mutations
🧠 RULE

“Components only display, they don’t decide.”

📄 9. PAGE RULES

📁 src/pages/

✅ ALLOWED
layout composition
calling hooks
UI orchestration
❌ FORBIDDEN
heavy logic
game rules
socket logic directly
🧠 RULE

“Pages glue everything together, they don’t compute.”

🔥 10. GAME FLOW RULE (MOST IMPORTANT)

You MUST always follow this flow:

UI → store/context → socket → backend → socket → store → UI

❌ NEVER:

UI → socket → game logic → UI (bad coupling)
⚠️ 11. SOCKET IS SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH
Only ONE socket instance
No multiple socket creations
No socket inside components directly
⚡ 12. NO DUPLICATE LOGIC RULE

If logic exists in:

game/
utils/
store/

👉 It must exist ONLY in ONE place.

🧠 13. TYPE SAFETY RULE
Every socket event MUST have a type
Every game state MUST have a type
No any in multiplayer logic